  "instructions": [
    "In a small bowl, mix paprika, sesame seeds, salt, and tandoori masala powder. Add whole milk or almond milk little by little until the mixture forms a dough.",
    "Grease a shallow dish with oil and place the dough in it. Press down to create an even layer.",
    "Preheat your oven to 375°F (190°C). Bake for about 10-12 minutes, or until golden brown.",
    "Cool slightly before serving."
